<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/483025-does-anyone-else-think-she-completely">Does anyone else think she completely ripped off another book/movie? As I read it I was thinking of a movie that I had seen years ago. I finally decided to look it up. Anyone think there are similarites to The Forgotten 
Garden and The Secret Garden.


http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1045518-secret_garden/</a>
</div>
