        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1324912361" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer3267752868837190354">I love these kind of stories. This is a wonderful tale, intricately woven through generations of different voices. I love the way the saga gently unfolds revealing bits and pieces at a time.<br/><br/><br/><br/>5 star -- a must read</span>

